Package: forestriesz
Type: Package
Title: Random-Forest Riesz Regression
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R: person("Alejandro", "Schuler", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "alejandro.schuler@gmail.com")
Description: R wrapper around the Python 'forestriesz' package — random-forest
    estimation of the Riesz representer of a linear functional, following
    Chernozhukov, Newey, Quintas-Martínez, Syrgkanis (2022). Sister package to
    'krrr' and 'rieszboost'. Reuses 'rieszreg' for estimand specification.
License: file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports:
    R6,
    reticulate (>= 1.30),
    rieszreg (>= 0.0.1)
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0),
    pkgload
Config/testthat/edition: 3
